'''李万熙'''（{{kor|k=이만희|hj=李萬熙}}；{{bd|1931年|9月15日}}），[[本貫|本貫]]{{link-ko|慶州李氏|경주 이씨}}，[[大韩民国|大韩民国]][[基督教|基督教]]系[[新兴宗教|新兴宗教]]团体“[[新天地耶稣教证据帐幕圣殿教会|新天地耶稣教证据帐幕圣殿教会]]”（SCJ）的创办人。<ref name="auto"><cite class="citation web">KOPETMAN, ROXANA. </cite></ref><ref name="thenational.ae"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.thenational.ae/uae/mystery-surrounds-visit-to-uae-of-alleged-religious-cult "Mystery surrounds visit to UAE of alleged religious cult - The National"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thenational.ae/uae/mystery-surrounds-visit-to-uae-of-alleged-religious-cult |date=20160930200417 }}. ''thenational.ae''.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALee+Man-hee&rft.atitle=Mystery+surrounds+visit+to+UAE+of+alleged+religious+cult+-+The+National&rft.genre=unknown&rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenational.ae%2Fuae%2Fmystery-surrounds-visit-to-uae-of-alleged-religious-cult&rft.jtitle=thenational.ae&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal"> </span></ref>

== 生平 ==
在1984年，李万熙成立新天地耶稣教证据帐幕圣殿教会（SCJ）<ref name="auto1"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.ecumenicalnews.com/article/contentious.christian.group.hosting.world.peace.summit.in.south.korea/26465.htm "Contentious Christian group hosting world peace summit in South Korea"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ecumenicalnews.com/article/contentious.christian.group.hosting.world.peace.summit.in.south.korea/26465.htm |date=20160310233809 }}. </cite></ref>，并作为“总会长”和组织领袖。 SCJ已经建立了其他几个组织，其中一些“附属组织”备受质疑。其中包括李万熙出任会长的“天上文化、世界和平、光的革命”（HWPL）、“国际和平青年组”（IPYG）、「Mannam」（或Mannam志愿者协会）、“Mannam国际青年联盟”和“国际妇女和平小组”（IWPG）。在这些组织将李万熙描绘成宗教冲突和战争、人权、青年和妇女权益保护中所谓的“和平使者”。<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://ireport.cnn.com/docs/DOC-1272161 "World Alliance of Religions' Peace (WARP) Summit In Korea a Monumental Success"] {{Wayback|url=http://ireport.cnn.com/docs/DOC-1272161 |date=20170201202238 }}. </cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://ireport.cnn.com/docs/DOC-1273864 "Heavenly World Peace Leadership Conference On Global Peace Leadership: Women, Youth and Interfaith Dialogue a Huge Success at the UN!"] {{Wayback|url=http://ireport.cnn.com/docs/DOC-1273864 |date=20170407134630 }}</cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.philstar.com/nation/2015/05/22/1457575/korean-peace-activists-join-maguindanao-peace-summit "Korean peace activists to join Maguindanao peace summit"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.philstar.com/nation/2015/05/22/1457575/korean-peace-activists-join-maguindanao-peace-summit |date=20160315055620 }}. ''philstar.com''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://thenationonlineng.net/lee-calls-for-implementation-of-cessation-of-war-convention/ "Lee calls for implementation of cessation of war convention - The Nation Nigeria"] {{Wayback|url=http://thenationonlineng.net/lee-calls-for-implementation-of-cessation-of-war-convention/ |date=20160503115912 }}. </cite></ref> 

2020年8月1日，李萬熙因涉嫌阻礙當局控制新型肺炎疫情擴散被南韓警方拘捕。<ref>[https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541237-20200801.htm 南韓拘捕「新天地教會」創辦人李萬熙][[RTHK|RTHK]].2020-08-01.</ref>

== 争议问题 ==
新天地耶稣教证据帐幕圣殿教会（SCJ）被指为邪教。<ref name="auto"/><ref name="thenational.ae"/><ref name="koreatimes.co.kr">{{cite web|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/09/293_164816.html|title=Controversial religious group holds int'l peace event in Seoul|author=|date=18 September 2014|work=koreatimes.co.kr|access-date=2016-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222151818/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/09/293_164816.html|archive-date=2015-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto3">{{cite news|last1=File|first1=Curtis|title=Mannam Volunteer Association faces criticism from foreign residents|url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2012/10/28/26/0302000000AEN20121028000200315F.HTML|accessdate=29 December 2015|agency=Yonhap News|date=28 October 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706085048/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2012/10/28/26/0302000000AEN20121028000200315F.HTML|archive-date=2017-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Controversial religious group holds int'l peace event in Seoul|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/09/293_164816.html|accessdate=29 December 2015|agency=Korea Times|date=18 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222151818/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/09/293_164816.html|archive-date=2015-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Valdez|first1=Matt|title=Shinchonji National Olympiad To Take Place In South Korea – Sept. 16|url=http://www.anaheimconnected.com/culture/shinchonji-national-olympiad-to-take-place-in-south-korea-sept-16/|accessdate=29 December 2015|agency=Anaheim Connected|date=10 September 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613160958/http://www.anaheimconnected.com/culture/shinchonji-national-olympiad-to-take-place-in-south-korea-sept-16/|archive-date=2016-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年新天地教会于9月17日至19日举办每四年一度的所谓“第六届世界宗教万国和平统一大会”。举办日期与李万熙的生日相同。<ref name="auto1"/>在这种情况下，他们同时邀请了很多国际宾客。这些宾客被告知他们被邀请参加“世界和平峰会”。由于庆祝活动和李万熙的生日庆祝在同一时间同一地点举办，很多被邀请者感到极大的困惑和尴尬。针对SCJ和它的“附属组织”，有一些曾经被欺骗的留学生，媒体和活动的其它曾经参与者在网上撰写新闻和文章抨击新天地教会的欺诈行为。<ref name="auto"/><ref name="thenational.ae"/><ref name="auto1"/><ref name="koreatimes.co.kr1"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/09/293_164816.html "Controversial religious group holds int'l peace event in Seoul"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2015/09/293_164816.html |date=20151222151818 }}. ''koreatimes.co.kr''. 18 September 2014.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALee+Man-hee&rft.atitle=Controversial+religious+group+holds+int%27l+peace+event+in+Seoul&rft.date=2014-09-18&rft.genre=unknown&rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreatimes.co.kr%2Fwww%2Fnews%2Fculture%2F2015%2F09%2F293_164816.html&rft.jtitle=koreatimes.co.kr&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal"> </span></ref><ref name="auto2"><cite class="citation news">File, Curtis (28 October 2012). </cite></ref>

2020年2月底，韩国检察院已对李万熙正式展开调查。韩国水原检察厅已将此案分配至刑事六部展开调查，理由是在新冠肺炎确诊者大幅度增加的情况下，李万熙阻碍保健当局的防疫活动<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202002/29/WS5e5a37fce4b05d1eff0b3b15.html |title=突破3000例，韩国“新天地”教主遭调查 |access-date=2020-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229143701/http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202002/29/WS5e5a37fce4b05d1eff0b3b15.html |archive-date=2020-02-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月1日，首尔市市长[[朴元淳|朴元淳]]促请檢察長[[尹碩律|尹碩律]]盡快下令逮捕李萬熙，如李萬熙及教會不行動，政府亦會以故意過失殺人罪對他進行刑事調查<ref>{{cite web|title=【新冠肺炎・韓國】新天地教主李萬熙被指「故意過失殺人」|publisher=香港01|date=2020-03-01|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/441862/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%99%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%8E%E8%90%AC%E7%86%99%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E6%95%85%E6%84%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%A4%B1%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA|access-date=2020-03-01|archive-date=2021-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804103631/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/441862/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%99%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%8E%E8%90%AC%E7%86%99%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E6%95%85%E6%84%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%A4%B1%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

3月2日，李万熙召开记者会，就大批教徒受感染，跪地向韩国国民道歉<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Seoul mayor sues South Korea religious group for 'murder' and 'injury' over spike in coronavirus cases|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/02/coronavirus-seoul-mayor-sues-south-korea-shincheonji-religious-group.html|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2020-03-02|last=Choudhury|first=Saheli Roy|work=CNBC|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303035627/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/02/coronavirus-seoul-mayor-sues-south-korea-shincheonji-religious-group.html|archive-date=2020-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据媒体报道，李万熙佩戴的手表印有鳳凰圖案和韩国前总统[[朴槿惠|朴槿惠]]的簽名。有分析称，李万熙和朴槿惠兩人關係匪淺，有可能是朴槿惠當年所給予的幫助，而李萬熙則在大選中出力以示回報<ref>{{Cite web|title=新天地会长跪地向国民谢罪 刻朴槿惠名字的手表亮了|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/03-02/9111194.shtml|accessdate=2021-01-15|work=[[中新网|中新网]]|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121063558/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/03-02/9111194.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=李万熙跪地谢罪手表抢镜：前总统纪念款|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_6276431|accessdate=2021-01-15|work=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]-The Paper|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121003704/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_6276431|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title="국민께 죄송"하다던 이만희 퇴장할 땐 '엄지 척'|url=https://news.joins.com/article/23720005|accessdate=2021-01-15|date=2020-03-02|work=중앙일보|language=ko|archive-date=2020-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302094442/https://news.joins.com/article/23720005|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

